it.eng.spagobi.meta.model.physical
Interface PhysicalForeignKey

All Superinterfaces:
ModelObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
PhysicalForeignKeyImpl
public interface PhysicalForeignKey
extends ModelObject

A representation of the model object 'Physical Foreign Key'.

The following features are supported:

  • Source Name
  • Source Table
  • Source Columns
  • Destination Name
  • Destination Table
  • Destination Columns
  • Model

See Also:
PhysicalModelPackage.getPhysicalForeignKey()
